Arsenal travel to Leicester City this weekend in the Premier League, seeking to end a run of poor results. The Gunners have thrown away leads against Crystal Palace, Wolves, etc recently and find themselves six points behind their hoss. Unai Emery also knows that a nine-point gap from Champions League spots, could see him lose his job at the Emirates.ac Kick off is 6.30pm West African time. Saturday, October 9
